thread.title_full: BRIEF-Logo Yazilim to merge with its units Sempa Bilgi, Intermat and Vardar | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Logo Yazilim to merge with its units Sempa Bilgi, Intermat and Vardar
text:
Oct 15 Logo Yazilim Sanayi ve Ticaret AS :
* To merge with its wholly owned units Sempa Bilgi Islem Sanayi ve Ticaret AS, Intermat Bilisim AS and Vardar Egitim Hizmetleri Yazilim Danismanlik ve Ticaret Sanayi AS Source text for Eikon:
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
